<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT47">
<l>naṉmaṇi vaṇṇaṉū rāḷiyuṅ kōḷariyum</l>
<l>poṉmaṇiyum muttamum pūmaramum paṉmaṇiṉī</l>
<l>rōṭu poruturuḷuṅ kāṉamum vāṉaramum</l>
<l>vēṭu muṭaivēṅ kaṭam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Veṅkaṭam,</l>
<l rend="indent">Which contains yāḷis, murderous lions, gold, gems, pearls, flowering trees,</l>
<l rend="indent">forests where many gems whirl around joining the waters,</l>
<l rend="indent">monkeys, and hunters,</l>
<l>is the town of the good sapphire-hued [Lord].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
